# itemIdentifier

**Instance Property**

The local identifier of the item.

## Declaration

```swift
var itemIdentifier: String? { get }
```

## Discussion

This value is `nil` if you create a Photos picker without a photo library.

## Inspecting a picker item

- **supportedContentTypes**: The content types the item supports in order of the most preferred to the least.
